import React, { useState } from 'react'; import { AlertTriangle, Clock, TrendingUp, Filter, Download, Search, AlertCircle, Package, Eye } from 'lucide-react'; const ReviewSpamPage = () => { const [selectedAlert, setSelectedAlert] = useState(null); const [filterPriority, setFilterPriority] = useState('all'); const spamReviews = [ { id: 'RA001', title: 'High-value return abuse', description: 'Customer initiated 12 returns in 30 days', customerId: 'C987654321', amount: '$4,567.89', category: 'Serial Returner', timeframe: '30 days ago', riskScore: 94, priority: 'high', riskLevel: 'High', investigationBrief: 'Customer has exhibited suspicious return behavior with multiple high-value items returned within warranty periods. Pattern suggests potential return fraud scheme.', riskIndicators: ['high_return_frequency', 'high_value_items', 'short_ownership_period'], subAgentResults: { returnFrequencyAnalysis: { score: 95, confidence: 'High' }, itemConditionAnalysis: { score: 88, confidence: 'Medium' }, customerBehaviorAnalysis: { score: 92, confidence: 'High' } } }, { id: 'RA002', title: 'Cross-category return pattern', description: 'Multiple returns across different product categories in short timeframe', customerId: 'C456789012', amount: '$1,234.56', category: 'Suspicious Pattern', timeframe: '14 days ago', riskScore: 76, priority: 'medium', riskLevel: 'Medium', investigationBrief: 'Customer returning items across multiple categories suggesting potential systematic abuse of return policy.', riskIndicators: ['cross_category_returns', 'timing_pattern', 'policy_exploitation'], subAgentResults: { returnFrequencyAnalysis: { score: 78, confidence: 'Medium' }, itemConditionAnalysis: { score: 72, confidence: 'Medium' }, customerBehaviorAnalysis: { score: 80, confidence: 'High' } } }, { id: 'RA003', title: 'Refund timing manipulation', description: 'Customer returns items just before warranty expiration', customerId: 'C123456789', amount: '$899.99', category: 'Policy Abuse', timeframe: '7 days ago', riskScore: 45, priority: 'low', riskLevel: 'Low', investigationBrief: 'Customer consistently returns items near warranty expiration dates, indicating potential timing manipulation.', riskIndicators: ['warranty_timing', 'pattern_recognition'], subAgentResults: { returnFrequencyAnalysis: { score: 48, confidence: 'Low' }, itemConditionAnalysis: { score: 42, confidence: 'Low' }, customerBehaviorAnalysis: { score: 45, confidence: 'Medium' } } } ]; const filteredAlerts = filterPriority === 'all' ? spamReviews : spamReviews.filter(alert => alert.priority === filterPriority); const handleAction = (id, action) => { console.log(`Action taken on ${id}: ${action}`); // Add actual implementation here }; const getPriorityColor = (priority) => { switch (priority) { case 'high': return 'bg-red-500 text-white'; case 'medium': return 'bg-orange-500 text-white'; case 'low': return 'bg-green-500 text-white'; default: return 'bg-gray-500 text-white'; } }; const getRiskScoreColor = (score) => { if (score >= 80) return 'text-red-400'; if (score >= 60) return 'text-orange-400'; return 'text-green-400'; }; return (

Medium Risk Cases

setSelectedAlert(review)} >

{review.description}

Customer ID: {review.customerId}
Amount: {review.amount}
Category: {review.category}
{review.timeframe}
Risk Score:
{review.riskScore}%
))}
); }; const InvestigationPanel = ({ selectedAlert, handleAction }) => { const getRiskColor = (riskLevel) => { switch (riskLevel) { case 'High': return 'bg-red-600/90 text-white border-red-400'; case 'Medium': return 'bg-yellow-500/90 text-black border-yellow-400'; case 'Low': return 'bg-green-500/90 text-white border-green-400'; default: return 'bg-neutral-700 text-white border-neutral-600'; } }; return (

Investigation Details

{selectedAlert.riskLevel} Risk

{selectedAlert.description}

Investigation Brief

{selectedAlert.investigationBrief}

Risk Indicators

{selectedAlert.riskIndicators.map((indicator, index) => ( {indicator.replace(/_/g, ' ').toUpperCase()} ))}

Sub-Agent Analysis

{Object.entries(selectedAlert.subAgentResults).map(([agent, result]) => (
{agent.replace(/([A-Z])/g, ' $1').trim()}
{result.score}%
{result.confidence} Confidence
))}
); }; export default ReviewSpamPage;
